{% from "macro.njk" import icon %}

<div
  class="prose-a:fancy-link prose-a:reset-text-color prose prose-zinc prose-teal dark:prose-invert"
>
  <h1 class="whitespace-nowrap font-mono">
    skorporaal.com<span class="inline-block -translate-x-1 animate-blink"
      >|</span
    >
  </h1>
  <p>
    Hello! My name is {{ site.name }}. I am currently a student of Software
    Development at the
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
      href="https://www.amsterdamuas.com"
      >Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences</a
    >'
    <a
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"
      href="https://www.amsterdamuas.com/faculty/fdmci/faculty-of-digital-media-and-creative-industries.html"
      >Faculty of Digital Media and Creative Industries</a
    >, the fruits of which you are reading this on.
  </p>

  <p>
    My goal is not just to improve what programming skills I already have, but
    to learn what programming as part of team is like and to how to contribute
    to creating a product for someone else instead of just myself.
  </p>

  <div class="not-prose mt-12 flex flex-row justify-center">
    <a
      class="flex w-min flex-row items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-700"
      target="_blank"
      rel="nofollower noreferrer noopener"
      href="{{ site.github }}"
    >
      {{ icon('github') }}
      <div class="ml-4 mr-6 underline">Hellrespawn</div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
